      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-rou-pri-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inizializzazione markers                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-prn-mrk-uno      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
