      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           release   srt-rec                                          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo su lettura sequenziale record [ocr]     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-srt-inp-220.
       stp-srt-inp-999.
           exit.

