           move      w-bas-qta-ass
                    (w-bas-ctr-001)       to   rf-ocp-qta-ass         .
           move      w-bas-dat-ass
                    (w-bas-ctr-001)       to   rf-ocp-dat-ass         .
           move      w-bas-prt-orf
                    (w-bas-ctr-001)       to   rf-ocp-prt-orf         .
