           if        d-qds-ros-qta-dsp    not  > zero
                     go to det-buf-dsp-160.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiornamento quantita' da spedire      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       d-qds-ros-qta-dsp    to   w-det-buf-dsp-wqs      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su lettura sequenziale record   *
      *                      * [osr]                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     det-buf-dsp-160.
       det-buf-dsp-180.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
