      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-buf-dsp-wqg    to   w-det-buf-dsp-wqd      .
           subtract  w-det-buf-dsp-wqs    from w-det-buf-dsp-wqd      .
           if        w-det-buf-dsp-wqd    <    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-buf-dsp-wqd      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Creazione elemento                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento numero elementi              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      1                    to   w-bds-num-ele          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Bufferizzazione elemento                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Data disponibilita'                 *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
