      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-buf-dsp-wqd    to   w-bds-qta-res
                                              (w-bds-num-ele)         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Protocollo ordine fornitore         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-bds-prt-orf
                                              (w-bds-num-ele)         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Progressivo riga ordine fornitore   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-bds-prg-orf
                                              (w-bds-num-ele)         .
       det-buf-dsp-200.
